<th class="summary" colspan="3" style="background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">Russian Civil War</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="3" style="text-align: center; font-size: 90%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; line-height: 1.5em;"><a href="/wiki/File:CWRArticleImage.jpg" class="image" title="CWRArticleImage.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3b/CWRArticleImage.jpg/300px-CWRArticleImage.jpg" width="300" height="382" border="0" /></a><br />
<b>Clockwise from top:</b> Soldiers of the <a href="/wiki/Don_Army" title="Don Army">Don Army</a> in 1919; a <a href="/wiki/White_Movement" title="White Movement" class="mw-redirect">White Russian</a> infantry division in March 1920; soldiers of the <a href="/wiki/1st_Cavalry_Army_(Soviet_Union)" title="1st Cavalry Army (Soviet Union)">1st Cavalry Army</a>; <a href="/wiki/Leon_Trotsky" title="Leon Trotsky">Leon Trotsky</a> in 1918; hanging of Bolsheviks by the <a href="/wiki/Czechoslovak_Legions" title="Czechoslovak Legions">Czechoslovak Corps</a>.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="3">
<table class="infobox" width="100%" style="margin: 0; cellpadding: 0; padding: 0; border: 0;">
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Date</th>
<td>1917 – 1923</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Location</th>
<td><span class="location">Former <a href="/wiki/Russian_Empire" title="Russian Empire">Russian Empire</a>, <a href="/wiki/Mongolia" title="Mongolia">Mongolia</a>, <a href="/wiki/Iran" title="Iran">Persia</a></span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Result</th>
<td>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Bolshevik" title="Bolshevik">Bolshevik</a> victory<br /></li>
<li>Establishment of the <a href="/wiki/Soviet_Union" title="Soviet Union">Soviet Union</a></li>
<li>Independence of <a href="/wiki/Estonia" title="Estonia">Estonia</a>, <a href="/wiki/Finland" title="Finland">Finland</a>, <a href="/wiki/Latvia" title="Latvia">Latvia</a>, <a href="/wiki/Lithuania" title="Lithuania">Lithuania</a> and <a href="/wiki/Poland" title="Poland">Poland</a></li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</td>
</tr>
